comments: James (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Robinson (MIA).
Green (LAL) is in a legal screening position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Adebayo (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact to the arm of Davis (LAL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.  Additionally, Adeyabyo does not take away Davis's landing area.
Green (LAL) makes contact to the ball and incidental contact to the hand of Butler (MIA) while it is in contact with the ball.
Green (LAL) ends his dribble and gathers the ball.  He then makes a pass, is the first player to touch the ball, and dribbles once again.
Nunn (MIA) moves into Green (LAL) delivering contact that affects Green's ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Green (LAL) is in a legal screening position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Adebayo (MIA).
Robinson (MIA) clamps Davis' (LAL) arm affecting Davis' ability to retrieve the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Butler (MIA).
Jones Jr. (MIA) moves legally alongside of James (LAL) not delivering contact as James loses control of the ball on his own.
Butler (MIA) does not intentionally kick the ball.
Green (LAL) is in a legal screening position as his arms remain inside the frame of his body and he does not deliver contact to Adebayo (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Davis (LAL).
Robinson (MIA) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (LAL).
Adebayo (MIA) and Davis (LAL) briefly engage and disengage as the two are attempting to retrieve the rebound.
Green (LAL) and Jones Jr. (MIA) briefly engage and disengage as the two are attempting to retrieve the rebound.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (LAL).
During the inbound pass, James (LAL) is late to the spot and initiates contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his FOM.
Adebayo (MIA) is in a legal screening position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Bradley (LAL).
Davis (LAL) moves into Butler's (MIA) space and makes contact to his body that affects his jump shot attempt.  The contact is not created by Butler's leg extension.
